asādo nāmārthaguṇa evāyaṃ | yad uktaṃ kaṇṭhābharaṇe || yat tu prākatyam arthasya prasādaḥ so bhidhīyata iti | yathā ayam udayati mudrābhaṃjanaḥ padminīnām ity ādāv anukto pi sūryya udayati padmamudrābhaṃjantvādinā ca lakṣyate | yady api kāvyapradīpe mukhyārtha iti nāmno doṣasyāyam udayati mudrābhaṃjana ity udāharaṇam upanyasta tathāpi niranubodhamukhyapadārthābhāve mukhyārtha iti doṣa ity avadhayaṃ  iha tu buddhādipadollekhe kṛte dakṣiṇapathapathikasārthānām anupādeyatā syāt kṛṣnādipadoddeśe tu tatkālakavalitamadoddhurāṇāṃ bauddhānām ity ubhayasādhāraṇya nopādeyatārthaṃ mukhyānuddeśo na doṣāya aṃnye tv āhuḥ kvacid viśeṣaṇam api viśeṣyapratipattikaraṃ || yathā nidhānagarbhām iva sāgarāmbarām itīhāpi jñānadāyāsiṃdhvādiviśeṣaṇaviśeṣyapratipatikaram ity adoṣaḥ śliṣṭarūpakākhyo yam alekāraḥ |
