>Ox-d.196(1)
graṃthakṛtsve bhitasiddhaye sveṣṭadevatāsevanarūpaṃ maṃgalam ācarati seti tacchabdopādānāt paramātmopalakṣyate atra śloko siṃdhor iti padena siṃdhuparamātmanoḥ śleṣaḥ pratipadaṃ jñeyaḥ bho dhīrāḥ saḥ śriye lakṣmyai amṛtāya muktaye ca sevyatāṃ akṣayaḥ kṣayarahitaḥ sa kaḥ yasya anaghāḥ nirmalāḥ guṇāḥ kiṃbhūtasya jñānadayāsiṃdhoḥ punaḥ kiṃbhūtasya agādhasya nityajñānānaṃdavairāgyādayaḥ nirmalāḥ pāpadukhavyasanakāmakopādidoṣarahitāḥ jñānaṃ muktisādhanaṃ | dayā nirupadhiparadukhaprahāṇechā tayoḥ siṃdhuḥ agādhasya kenāpy ajñānamahimnaḥ || 1 ||

>Ox-d.196(2)
anaghā bhavadbhiḥ sa dhīrāḥ sevyatāṃ na aghaṃ pāpeyāṃ te 'naghā niḥpāpāḥ sukṛtina iti yāvat_ dhiyaṃ rāti dadāti iti dhīrāḥ | dhīrā jñānaprado gurur iti kośaḥ prayojanam anuddiśya mando pi na pravarttata iti gurur iti sevāyāḥ phalam āha śriye cāmṛtāya ceti ca dvayam ubhayoḥ prādhānyadyotanāya nanu guro śriyo bhāvā tataḥ kathaṃ sā prāpyate ity āśaṃkyāha yasyeti a sa guror ā lakṣmī guṇāś ca saṃti tad uktaṃ satyaṃ śaucaṃ dayā kṣāṃtis tyāgaḥ saṃtoṣa ārjjavaṃ śamo damas tapaḥ sāmyaṃ titikṣoparatiḥ śrutaṃ jñānaṃ viraktaraiś caryaṃ śauryyaṃ tejo balaṃ smṛtiḥ svātaṃtryaṃ kauśalyaṃ kānti dhairyyamārdavam eva cety ādayo guṇāḥ kīdṛśasya jñānadayāsiṃdhoḥ jñāyate 'neneti jñānaśāstraṃ dayā niṣkāraṇaparaduḥkhaprahāṇechā kīdṛśasya na gādhaḥ talasparśo yasya gaṃbhīrasya yad vā agaṃ śaityaṃ vṛkṣaṃ vāpnotīti agātaṃ manasā dadhātīty agādhaḥ tasya viṣṇubhaktasyeti yāvat_ kīdṛśo dhīrāḥ akṣayaḥ aḥ vāsudevas tasmin_ kṣayo nivāso jñānaṃ vāso kṣayaḥ atha vā sa dhīrā mayā sevyatāṃ saḥ kaḥ yasya guṇāḥ anaghāḥ na aghaṃ yebhyas te 'naghāḥ śeṣaṃ samānaṃ yad vā he dhīrāḥ saḥ bhagavān_ sevyatāṃ ārādhyatāṃ saḥ kaḥ yasya guṇāḥ maitrīmaryādādayo 'ṇimādayo vā anaghāḥ yad vā anaghāḥ hṛdyāḥ anagho pāpahṛdyayor iti dharaṇiḥ kiṃbh3utasya jñānadayāsiṃdhoḥ jñānaṃ samastaviṣayāvabodhaḥ svārtham anapekṣya paraduḥkhaprahāṇechā dayā tasya agādhasyānavachinnamahimnaḥ kiṃbhūtaḥ parahitāpādānodeṣu nāsti kṣayo virāmo yasya so kṣayaḥ kasmai śriye cāmṛtāya ca śrīr atra trivargasaṃprāptiḥ amṛtāya mokṣāya ca 1

>Ox-c.31
yasya bhagavataḥ jñānadayayor bodhakaruṇayoḥ siṃdhoḥ samudrasyeva gaṃbhīrasyāgādhasyānyair aprāptajñānadayāvadheḥ anaghāḥ niṣpāpāḥ guṇāḥ kṣāṃtyādayo bodhipakṣyāḥ saptaviṃśat_ so 'kṣayo kṣobhyo jāto mārajittvāt || anaṃtajñānasaṃtāno vā | bho dhīrāḥ yoginaḥ dhyeyaṃ prati dhiyaṃ īrayaṃtīti kṛtvā śriyo bhogārtha avidyamānaṃ mṛtaṃ maraṇaṃ yatrety amṛtāya mokṣārthaṃ ca sevyatām ārādhyataṃ | leśaspṛṣṭo pi samudro pi viṣṇoḥ kṣayo nivāsaḥ agādho talasparśaḥ ratnādimatvān nirmalaguṇaḥ lakṣmarthaṃ pīyūṣārthaṃ suraiḥ sevitaḥ || 1 || iti graṃthāraṃbhe bhīpsitasiddhihetuṃ jinam anusmṛtya

