>RAS-T144
graṃthāraṃbhe vighnavighātāyābhimatadevatānamaskāreṇa dharmmam utpādayan_ śaivavaiṣṇavabauddhān_ pravarttayituṃ śiṣyaśikṣāyai cādau nibadhnāti yasyetyādi | asyārthaḥ he dhīrā a viṣṇuḥ sevyatāṃ akāro vāsudeva syād ākāras tu pitāmahaḥ | ity ākṣarakoṣaḥ | yad vā he dhīrāḥ sa siṃdhur viṣnuḥ sevyatāṃ | sindhuḥ samudre 'nante ca siṃdhur nadyāṃ mahānasa iti dharaṇiḥ || yasya siṃdhau guṇā jagadavanaduṣṭanivāraṇādayaḥ anaghāḥ apāpāḥ anagho apāpākutsayor iti dharaṇiḥ | kīdṛśasya jñānadayāsiṃdhoḥ jñanaṃ vastutatvāvabodhaḥ nirupādhiparaduḥkhaharaṇechā dayā tābhyāṃ tayor vā siṃdhur iva siṃdhuḥ | atas tasya sevaivocitaheti bhāvaḥ | yad vā jñāna dadātīti jñānadā sarasvatī tayā sahitā ī lakṣmīr jñānade madhyapadalopī samāsaḥ | tayā viśiṣṭasya lakṣmīsarasvatīyuktasyety arthaḥ | lakṣmīr īkāra ucyata ity kāṣaḥ | agādhasya anavagāhyamahimnaḥ | kīdṛśaḥ akṣayaḥ na vidyate kṣayo vināśo yasya nityatvāt | sevāphalam āha śriya iti śriye trivargasaṃpatyai tathā ca vyāḍiḥ | lakṣmī sarasvatī dhī trivargasaṃpatibhūtiśobhāsūpakaraṇaveśaracanāguṇeṣv api śrī prathiteti amṛtāya mokṣāyety arthaḥ | atas tasya sevayā sakalapuruṣārthasiddhir iti | ḍata vā he dhīrāḥ sa siṃdhuḥ samudraḥ sevyatāṃ | yasya guṇā dhairyyagāṃbhīryyādayaḥ anaghā vyasanarahitāḥ paramotkarṣānn iti yāvat_ duḥkhavyasaneṣv agham ity amaraḥ | kīdṛśasya jñānaṃ dadātīti jñānadā gaṃgā tayā viśiṣṭasya nadīpatitvāt | ato gaṃgāpatitvāt tasya sevaivocitā tasyā hi smaraṇād eva vicitrabhavanavicitrābharaṇārogyasukhasaṃpattayo bhavaṃti | ato 'sya sevayā kin na syāt | punaḥ kīdṛśasya agādhasya atalasparśasya sa kīdṛśaḥ akṣayaḥ sadā saṃpūrṇaḥ | yad vā asya viṣṇoḥ kṣayo nivāso yatra kṣayo vasati sthānaṃ kṣinivāsagatyor ity asya bhāve 'dhikaraṇe vā nirūpaṃ | sevāphalam aha śriye lakṣmai amṛtāya mokṣāya pīyūṣāya ity arthaḥ | yad vā dhīr buddhis tāṃ rāti dadātīti āto man_kvanivvanivvic iti vicapratyaye kīlālapāvad dhīrāśabdo graṃtham abhidhatte || sa dhīrāṃ graṃtha sevyatāṃ satatam anuśīlyatāṃ yasya dhīro graṃthasya guṇā vyutpattikaraṇayaśaskaratvāda